{"tid":598935,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【代繳DSE費】剔除自修生　楊潤雄指是無奈決定　稱行政安排困難","createTime":"2018-03-20T03:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T05:46:57.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"755f4640bbd0bb212ed2ffbc8c5b411b95fc5dd4","tid":598935,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T03:46:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180320/s00001/8e411714d378011ab6d18f351c82e505.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180320%2Fs00001%2F8e411714d378011ab6d18f351c82e505.jpg&h=1189ca9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《財政預算案》提出為參加2019年中學文憑試（DSE）考生代繳考試費，財政司長陳茂波當時指要支持自修生，但在外界憂慮措施被濫用下，教育局長楊潤雄日前決定代繳考試費範圍收窄至學校考生。他今早在商台節目形容，該決定是無可奈何。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄在節目指出，《預算案》提出為文憑試考生代繳考試費原意是希望幫得愈多人愈好，但無法排除有人參加考試藉機影響考生，對考生構成心理壓力，而且行政安排上有困難，故平衡各種因素後，「無可奈何」將代繳措施收窄至學校考生。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄表示，明白部分自修生會感到「原本有的變了無」，惟考生考試環境會相對穩定。<br />\n<br />\n主持總結時稱「事前想清楚好緊要」，楊潤雄聞言發出笑聲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180320/s00001/1521515950425\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180320%2Fs00001%2F1521515950425&d=D%2BverwI54%2FCFhfeffaWAvrZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=d02b7771\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180320%2Fs00001%2F1521515950425&h=f701b380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180320/s00001/1521515950425</a>"},{"pid":"3382fcfb4d6f46b0a57c9fb274f6af110201a00b","tid":598935,"uid":5159,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T03:47:58.000Z","msg":"限年齡自修生咪得囉, 多極有限 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17da4a9d34b757724e0e286731268c44ad9ddcf","tid":598935,"uid":106506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T03:49:06.